These are Puzzles for 7x2 Level 1

.:: Puzzle 7x2-Level-1-1::.
The people's birthday is in 2 different months: september, november
The people have 2 different hobbies: puzzles, sudoku
The people have 2 different jobs:  fisherman, mechanic
The people perfer 2 different movie-genres: superhero, western
2 different brands of cigars are smoked: aristoff, dunhill
2 different pets are kept: frog, turtle
There are 2 different favourite colors: green, aquamarine
1. the person who's birthday is in september is on the far right##1
2. the mechanic is on the far right##1
3. the person who likes aquamarine is on the left of the person who's hobby is sudoku##1
4. the owner of the frog is the dunhill-smoker##1
5. the person watching western movies is on the far left##1
6. the owner of the turtle is on the right of the person who likes aquamarine##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |     2      |
| Birthday      | november     | september       |
| Hobby         | puzzles   | sudoku     |
| Job           | fisherman | mechanic   |
| Movie-Genre   | western   | superhero  |
| Cigar   | dunhill | aristoff |
| Pet           | frog      | turtle     |
| Color     | aquamarine    | green   |

