.:: Puzzle 7x2-Level-1-2::.
There are 2 different favourite beverages: almond-milk, iced-tea
The people have 2 different hobbies: dancing, drawing
The people have 2 different jobs:  police-officer, teacher
2 different games are played: mah-jongg, backgammon
There 2 different types of food: apricot, onion
There are 2 different favourite colors: blue, aquamarine
The people use 2 different means of transport: tram, van
1. the teacher is on the right of the person who's hobby is drawing##1
2. the person who likes aquamarine is the person driving the van##1
3. the person driving the tram is on the left of the person playing mah-jongg##1
4. the person eating onion is on the far right##1
5. the person drinking almond-milk is the person who likes blue##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |       1        |    2     |
| Beverage      | almond-milk    | iced-tea |
| Hobby         | drawing        | dancing  |
| Job           | police-officer | teacher  |
| Game   | backgammon            | mah-jongg    |
| Food   | apricot     | onion   |
| Color           | blue         | aquamarine    |
| Transport     | tram           | van      |

