There 2 different types of food: eggplant, strawberry
The people have 2 different jobs:  dancer, journalist
The people perfer 2 different movie-genres: martial-arts, spy
2 different pets are kept: hamster, pony
The people prefer 2 different music-genres: salsa, folk
The people have 2 different hobbies: skydiving, singing
1. the owner of the pony is on the right of the fan of salsa##1
2. the person playing go is on the right of the person watching martial-arts movies##1
3. the person eating eggplant is on the right of the person who's hobby is skydiving##1
4. the dancer is on the right of the person who's hobby is skydiving##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1       |     2      |
| Game      | whist          | go       |
| Food          | strawberry   | eggplant   |
| Job           | journalist   | dancer     |
| Movie-Genre   | martial-arts | spy        |
| Pet           | hamster      | pony       |
| Music-Genre         | salsa       | folk |
| Hobby     | skydiving          | singing |

