2. the person who's hobby is hiking is on the right of the person traveling to miami##1
3. the argentine is the person traveling to miami##1
4. the ritmeester-smoker is on the right of the person who's hobby is card-games##1
5. the person who growsbellflower is on the left of the person driving the train##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |     2     |
| Hobby         | card-games  | hiking    |
| Cigar           | alhambra       | ritmeester    |
